  "description": "A close-up, top-down view of the interior of a vibrant orange tulip flower. The petals are partially visible, curving inward and showcasing a smooth texture. The flower\u2019s reproductive parts are centered, featuring a pale yellow pistil surrounded by dark brown anthers. Green sepals form a star-like base for the stamens. The focus is sharp on the flower\u2019s center, with a shallow depth of field softening the petal edges and background, suggesting a natural and organic setting.",
